'''2016年洛克哈特热气球坠毁事故'''發生於2016年7月30日，一架热气球在[[美国|美国]][[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]首府[[奥斯丁|奥斯丁]]以南30英里处（约50公里）[[洛克哈特|洛克哈特]]附近的非建制社区麦斯韦尔起火坠毁，16名乘员遇难。这是美国伤亡最惨重的热气球灾难和自2009年[[科尔根航空3407号班机|科尔根航空3407号班机]]以来美国本土死伤最严重的航空事故，也是全球仅次于2013年[[埃及卢克索热气球事故|埃及卢克索热气球事故]]的损失第二大惨重的热气球事故<ref name="BNO">{{cite news |url=http://bnonews.com/news/index.php/news/id4979 |title=16 feared dead after hot air balloon crash in central Texas |date=2016-07-30 |work=BNO News |access-date=2016-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160731182929/http://bnonews.com/news/index.php/news/id4979 |archive-date=2016-07-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 航空器 ==
涉事航空器属Kubicek BB85Z型热气球<ref name=KXAN310716>{{cite web |url=http://kxan.com/2016/07/31/ntsb-team-arrives-in-lockhart-today/ |title=NTSB: Hot air balloon made contact with a utility wire |first1=Patrick |last1=Tolbert |first2=Cathy |last2=Bien |publisher=LIN Television of Texas |work=KXAN |date=2016-07-31 |accessdate=2016-08-01 |archive-date=2016-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803082904/http://kxan.com/2016/07/31/ntsb-team-arrives-in-lockhart-today/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[飞机注册编号|注册编号]]N2469L，{{le|制造商序列号|Serial code}}1076<ref name=ASN188936>{{cite web |url=https://aviation-safety.net/wikibase/wiki.php?id=188936 |title=ASN Wikibase Occurrence #188936 |publisher=Aviation Safety Network |date=2016-07-30 |accessdate=2016-08-01 |archive-date=2016-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816052850/https://aviation-safety.net/wikibase/wiki.php?id=188936 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它隶属于大奥斯丁地区的德克萨斯州之心气球旅行公司({{lang|en|Heart of Texas Balloon Ride}}）<ref name=BBC36933150>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-36933150 |title=Texas hot air balloon crash: 'No survivors' among 16 on board |publisher=BBC News Online |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2016-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160731061342/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-36933150 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 事故 ==
[[北美中部時區|当地时间]]7时40分（12:40 [[UTC|UTC]]），气球在德克萨斯州[[洛克哈特|洛克哈特]]附近的一块田地坠毁，所有乘客遇难。气球被附近的电线拦下，据报救援人员赶到现场时篮子曾冒火。7时44分，救援服务接到“疑似车辆事故”的报警<ref name=Sky10517549>{{cite web |url=http://news.sky.com/story/hot-air-balloon-crash-kills-16-people-in-texas-10517549 |title=Hot Air Balloon Crash Kills 16 People In Texas |publisher=Sky News |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2016-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730174014/http://news.sky.com/story/hot-air-balloon-crash-kills-16-people-in-texas-10517549 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/CCTXOEM/photos/a.424186777669052.1073741829.382284801859250/1055655947855462/?type=3&theater|title=Caldwell County Office of Emergency Management|accessdate=2016-07-30|archive-date=2019-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214165058/https://www.facebook.com/CCTXOEM/photos/a.424186777669052.1073741829.382284801859250/1055655947855462/?type=3&theater|dead-url=no}}</ref>。抵达后，救援人员表示据报着火的“明显”是热气球的吊篮部分。目击者称听到两下“噼啪”声时曾以为是枪声。报告称热气球在原定一个小时的飞行将近过半时失联。据认为，气球与电线相撞<ref name=LPR>{{cite web |url=http://post-register.com/local-news/16-believe-killed-in-balloon-incident/ |title=16 believed killed in balloon incident |first=Kathi |last=Bliss |publisher=Lockhart Post-Register |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2016-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804032710/http://post-register.com/local-news/16-believe-killed-in-balloon-incident/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。气球的塑料皮落在起火吊篮东北方1210米处，航空器覆盖了约15公里的距离<ref name=KXAN310716/>。

== 调查 ==
[[联邦航空管理局|联邦航空管理局]]派出调查人员前往现场。[[国家运输安全委员会|国家运输安全委员会]]将接管他们的调查。[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]人员到场为运输委员会的调查保存证物<ref name=CNN300716>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/30/us/texas-hot-air-balloon-crash/index.html |title=Hot air balloon with 16 aboard crashes in Texas; no survivors |first1=Stephen |last1=Visser |first2=John |last2=Newsome |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2016-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730170249/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/30/us/texas-hot-air-balloon-crash/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。事件被委员会定性为“重大事故”<ref name=ABC41015210>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/hot-air-balloon-carrying-16-people-crashes-texas-41015210 |title='Number of Fatalities' in Texas Balloon Crash; Toll Unclear |first=Jim |last=Vertuno |publisher=ABC News |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2016-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160731211310/http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/hot-air-balloon-carrying-16-people-crashes-texas-41015210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。废墟中有14台私人电子设备（手机、一台[[iPad|iPad]]和多台摄像机）被检获，均交由联邦调查局恢复数据<ref name=KXAN310716/>。

德克萨斯州公共安全部在初步调查报告中表示，调查人员相信热气球是撞上电线而起火的<ref name=CNN300716/>。

== 后续 ==
8月1日，老板在事件中遇难的涉事公司宣布暂停营业<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/08/01/us/texas-hot-air-balloon-crash/index.html|title=Hot air balloon crash: Company suspends operations|first1=Polo|last1=Sandoval|first2=Melissa|last2=Gray|first3=Holly|last3=Yan|website=CNN|date=2016-08-01|access-date=2016-08-01|archive-date=2016-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801194030/http://www.cnn.com/2016/08/01/us/texas-hot-air-balloon-crash/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hothotairballoonrides.com/|title=Hot Hot Air Balloon Rides|website=Heart of Texas Hot Air Balloon Rides|date=2016-08-01|access-date=2016-08-02|archive-date=2016-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801162403/http://www.hothotairballoonrides.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

